      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPENCER BANNER (5) sizzled around this track over 520m in 29.64 for a 2.5 lengths victory. Has the ability and expected to go close again. ZIPPING BUFFALO (2) has a strong record here including two wins from four starts. Below best last time at Nowra (30.54) in a Grade 5, finishing a 12 length fifth. Makes strong appeal on best. SAHARA PEARL (1) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth (30.19) in a Grade 5 at The Gardens. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. One of the main contenders. ZIPPING VIOLET (8) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
